Parliament, Monday, 27 February 2023 – The Portfolio Committee on Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities will tomorrow be briefed by the Department of Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities on the National Council on Gender-Based Violence and Femicide Bill.
	
	Details of the meeting:
	Date: 28 February 2023 (Wednesday)
	Time: 9:30am– 13:00pm
	Venue: Southern Sun, Cullinan, Cape Town
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES
	
	For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
	Name: Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Cell: 081 497 4694
